Fans and industry peers are mourning the death of rapper Rikhado Makhado, popularly known as Riky Rick. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu takes a look at a life that was. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Another death in the entertainment industry, just two weeks after the passing of media personality Kuli Roberts. Fans and industry peers are mourning the death of rapper Rikhado Makhado, popularly known as Riky Rick. READ: Riky Rick dies aged 34 The 34-year-old took his life on Wednesday morning. He had openly talked about his battle with depression. WATCH: Riky Rick remembered as visionary artist In a statement, the Makhado family has thanked the country for its messages of support and has asked for privacy as they try to come to terms with his death. Details of the funeral and memorial will be confirmed in due course. * eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu reports.